x509: Provides an implementation of a subset of the X.509 RFC 5280.

This module provides a certificate parser, public and private key parsers,
and tools to verify trust paths of certificate chains.

The module is work in progress. It is still missing features for certain
certificate extensions like name constraints and policy constraints.
Certificate creation and support for certification revocation lists is also
still missing.

Be advised that Hare's cryptography implementations have not been audited.
